; Regression test for issue #616: bal --amount-data fails wrong (BZ#616)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/616
;
; Bug: bal --amount-data outputs the period-end date for all account entries
; instead of the actual transaction dates. The date shown (one day before -e)
; is wrong; each account should reflect the date of its last posting.
; Compare: reg --amount-data correctly shows per-posting dates.

2024/01/01 First Expense
    Expenses:Food          $10.00
    Assets:Cash

2024/06/15 Second Expense
    Expenses:Food          $20.00
    Assets:Cash

test bal --amount-data -e 2025/01/01 Expenses
2024-12-31 30
end test
